On Thursday it was announced that, [after much
criticism,](https://globalvoicesonline.org/2010/08/03/chile-isabel-allende-
and-the-national-prize-for-literature/) Isabel Allende was the winner of the
2010 Chilean National Prize for Literature. Julio Suarez Anturi [thinks [es]
](http://juliosuarezanturi.wordpress.com/2010/09/03/las-criticas-a-isabel-
nacen-de-la-envidia/)that the criticism she receives from other writers and
intellectuals who think she did not deserve the price is born of envy.

